name: SwiftTwitch
summary: Wrapper for the New Twitch API written in Swift.
description:
SwiftTwitch allows for accessing the Twitch API is a typed, safe, and readable way. To view a proper
usage document of SwiftTwitch, please view the GitHub README available here: https://bitbucket.devops.nonprod.empf.local/scm/react/SwiftTwitch.git
